high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter by the sink.
Pick up an apple on the counter.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator.
Chill the apple in the refrigerator.
Turn and go to the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter on the right side of the stove.
Pick up the apple on the left side of the bread.
Turn around and go to the front of the refrigerator.
Chill the apple on the middle shelf in the refrigerator and take it out.
Go to the microwave on the counter top on the right.
Place the apple inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right and walk forward to face the right end of the counter.
Pick up the apple on the counter.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the fridge.
Cool the apple in the fridge and then remove it.
Take a step to the right to face the microwave on the counter.
Place the apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To cool an apple as well as place it in the microwave.
